 * @return turn Kampsvinget, hvor entitet dukkede op.
 */
function getBirthTurn(integer|real entity) => integer;
function getBirthTurn() => integer;

/**
 * @brief (No `func_getBulbType` in doc lang — add an entry to match the client Documentation tab.)
